description:
Created by Justice Action Media https://vimeo.com/justiceactionmedia and Maverick Media: https://maverickmedia.wordpress.com/ 

Interview with Peter Dale Scott, professor at U.C. Berkeley for decades, poet and author, by Cindy Piester of Pulse TV in Ventura, CA. Discuss Scott's most recent book, "American War Machine:Deep Politics, the CIA Global Drug Connection, and the Road to Afghanistan".

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
